OL,5,G1200 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FThe cops deal with a major drugs
OL,7,     Fbust, a man linked to an alleged
OL,8,     Fassault on a woman, and a gang of
OL,9,     Fsuspected poachers with an
OL,10,     Fun-taxed van.
OL,11,G1300 Traffic Cops
OL,12,     FOver a Bank Holiday, near
OL,13,     FScarborough, a high-speed pursuit
OL,14,     Fensues after a driver fails to
OL,15,     Fstop. In the Dales, an operation
OL,16,     Fis underway to crack down on
OL,17,     Fmotorists flouting the law.
OL,18,G1400 Police Interceptors
OL,19,     FThe interceptors come knocking for
OL,20,     Fa suspected drugs dealer who's
OL,21,     Fbeen on the run for two years.
