OL,5,G1500 Police Interceptors
OL,6,     FWhen a dog handler is taken out of
OL,7,     Fthe chase, multiple cops and the
OL,8,     Fpolice chopper take up the hunt
OL,9,     Ffor a driver who flees on foot.
OL,10,G1600 Police Interceptors
OL,11,     FLisa and Jim find themselves
OL,12,     Fslipping and sliding through the
OL,13,     Fpitch black on the trail of a
OL,14,     Frunaway 4x4. Their suspect seems
OL,15,     Fto know rural Nottinghamshire like
OL,16,     Fthe back of his hand .
