OL,5,G1700 Shoplifters: Caught Red Handed
OL,6,     FUndercover detectives Steve and
OL,7,     FAdam overhear two people
OL,8,     Fdiscussing what they have just
OL,9,     Fshoplifted. The team go in pursuit
OL,10,     Fbut the suspected stolen goods are
OL,11,     Fnowhere to be seen. (Ep4)
OL,12,G1800 Home and Away
OL,13,     FMackenzie and Levi struggle to
OL,14,     Fprocess their grief. Lacey worries
OL,15,     Ffor her dad. Richie visits David.
OL,16,G1830 Home and Away
OL,17,     FDavid confides in Amelia. Beau
OL,18,     Fwants Harper all to himself.
OL,19,     FRichie makes a tough decision.
