OL,5,G1900 GPs: Behind Closed Doors
OL,6,     FIn Peterborough, a pair of cyclist
OL,7,     Fbrothers receive medical support
OL,8,     Fafter being knocked off their
OL,9,     Fbikes by a van, and Dr Devin Gray
OL,10,     Fis concerned about a patient's
OL,11,     Fdramatic weight loss.
OL,12,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,13,     FJunior Doctor Tom's first patient
OL,14,     Fis 18-year-old Lewis who has
OL,15,     Fbroken bones and deep wounds from
OL,16,     Fa moped accident - but causing him
OL,17,     Fthe most pain is his fear of
OL,18,     Fneedles.
